        <Parent_String>architectural moldings by location or context [300003558], architectural moldings [300244017], moldings and molding components for architecture [300052382], surface elements (architectural) [300001987], surface elements and surface element components [300078075], architectural elements [300000885], components by specific context [300241584], components (objects parts) [300241583], Components (hierarchy name) [300241490], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
